        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3EReference%20Hex%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22refcont%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22refleft%22%20style%3D%22position%3Arelative%3B%20top%3A70px%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Ch2%20style%3D%22padding-left%3A25px%22%3EAnatomy%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20easy%20to%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20Library%20of%20Babel%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%2C%20this%20is%20by%20design.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20do%20my%20best%20here%20to%20orient%20new%20users%2C%20and%20help%20them%20make%20use%20of%20its%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20universe%20(which%20others%20call%20the%20Library)%20is%20composed%20of%20an%20indefinite%2C%20perhaps%20infinite%20number%20of%20hexagonal%20galleries%E2%80%A6The%20arrangement%20of%20the%20galleries%20is%20always%20the%20same%3A%20Twenty%20bookshelves%2C%20five%20to%20each%20side%2C%20line%20four%20of%20the%20hexagon's%20six%20sides%E2%80%A6each%20bookshelf%20holds%20thirty-two%20books%20identical%20in%20format%3B%20each%20book%20contains%20four%20hundred%20ten%20pages%3B%20each%20page%2C%20forty%20lines%3B%20each%20line%2C%20approximately%20eighty%20black%20letters%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EWith%20these%20words%2C%20Borges%20has%20set%20the%20rule%20for%20the%20universe%20%3Ci%3Een%20abyme%3C%2Fi%3E%20contained%20on%20our%20site.%20Each%20book%20has%20been%20assigned%20its%20particular%20hexagon%2C%20wall%2C%20shelf%2C%20and%20volume%20code.%20The%20somewhat%20cryptic%20strings%20of%20characters%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20on%20the%20book%20and%20browse%20pages%20identify%20these%20locations.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Fbook.cgi%3Fjeb0110jlb-w2-s4-v16%22%20class%3D%22intext%22%3Ejeb0110jlb-w2-s4-v16%3C%2Fa%3E%20means%20the%20book%20you%20are%20reading%20is%20the%2016th%20volume%20(v16)%20on%20the%20fourth%20shelf%20(s4)%20of%20the%20second%20wall%20(w2)%20of%20hexagon%20jeb0110jlb.%20Consider%20it%20the%20Library%20of%20Babel's%20equivalent%20of%20the%20Dewey%20Decimal%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22refright2%22%20style%3D%22position%3Arelative%3B%20top%3A123px%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cimg%20class%3D%22mobiledrop%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20left%3A15px%3B%22%20alt%3D%22An%20engraving%20by%20Juan%20de%20Amusco%20Valverde%2C%20'Historia%20de%20la%20composicion%20del%20cuerpo%20humano'%2C%20from%201551.%20A%20human%20figure%20has%20flayed%20itself%20to%20display%20its%20musculature.%22%20title%3D%22'Historia%20de%20la%20composicion%20del%20cuerpo%20humano'%20by%20Juan%20de%20Amusco%20Valverde%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Chr%20style%3D%22clear%3Aboth%3B%20width%3A%2085%25%3B%20position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A200px%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22refleft%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A320px%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hexagon%20names%20contain%20letters%20and%20numbers.%20This%20makes%20them%20in%20effect%20a%20base-36%20system%20for%20identifying%20unique%20locations%20in%20the%20library.%20Nonetheless%2C%20hexagon%20names%20still%20commonly%20stretch%20to%20more%20than%203200%20characters.%20(For%20reasons%20I%20do%20not%20fully%20understand%2C%20but%20which%20I%20believe%20to%20be%20merely%20statistical%2C%20books%20found%20by%20searching%20almost%20always%20contain%20hexagon%20names%20of%203254%20characters.)%20Because%20of%20their%20length%2C%20it's%20not%20possible%20for%20all%20browsers%20to%20access%20them%20using%20what%E2%80%99s%20known%20as%20a%20GET%20request.%20The%20only%20effect%20this%20should%20have%20for%20users%20is%20that%20books%20in%20hexagons%20with%20names%20of%20greater%20than%201950%20characters%20can%20only%20be%20bookmarked%20by%20using%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbookmarkable%E2%80%9D%20link%20on%20the%20book%20pages.%20It%20allows%20you%20to%20create%20a%20custom%20url%20for%20pages%20and%20share%20them%20as%20links%20or%20bookmark%20them.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20only%20way%20to%20recover%20a%20book%20you%20have%20checked%20out%20in%20the%20past%20is%20to%20copy%20down%20its%20hexagon-wall-shelf-volume%20identifier%20and%20page%20number.%20These%20can%20be%20entered%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Fbrowse.cgi%22%20class%3D%22intext%22%3Ebrowse%3C%2Fa%3E%20page%20to%20access%20any%20book%20by%20its%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22refright%22%20style%3D%22position%3Arelative%3B%20top%3A320px%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22incidental%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A-1px%3B%22%3EOne%20caveat%3A%20because%20of%20their%20length%2C%20hexagon%20names%20often%20appear%20in%20truncated%20form%20on%20the%20site.%20In%20order%20to%20obtain%20the%20full%20hexagon%20name%2C%20either%20download%20the%20book%20(its%20location%20will%20be%20printed%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20text%20document)%20or%20follow%20the%20book%20location%20link%20to%20the%20browse%20page.%20Both%20of%20these%20links%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20navigation%20bar%20of%20any%20book%20you%20access.%20The%20first%20link%20in%20that%20list%20is%20an%20abbreviated%20version%20of%20the%20book%20location%2C%20and%20allows%20you%20to%20browse%20the%20shelf%20containing%20the%20book%20you%20are%20currently%20reading.%20The%20browse%20page%20will%20contain%20the%20full%20hexagon%20name%20in%20a%20copy-pastable%20form%20in%20its%20text%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22incidental%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20relative%3B%20top%3A-7px%3B%22%3EThe%20library%20offer